premise_source_doc_sentence: He rose to fame in the late 1990s with the release of his sophomore album My Way  (  1997  )  , which spawned his first U.S. Billboard Hot 100 number-one single , `` Nice & Slow '' , amongst top-two singles `` You Make Me Wan na ... '' and `` My Way '' .
He rose to fame after the release of his sophomore album My Way  (  1997  )  and earned Grammy Award nominations for `` You Make Me Wan na '' and `` My Way '' as Best Male R&B Vocal performance .
